ink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/from-the-gulf-war-to-gaza-israel-must-not-make-americas-mistakes/0000018b-7974-d4a8-a3cf-fdfd4a2a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列 DJ 在演奏最后一首歌曲时被哈马斯杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/these-djs-survived-hamas-massacre-to-tell-the-tale-and-play-another-set/0000018b-7351-d4a8-a3cf-fff9e9380000</link><description>至少有 260 人在加沙边境附近的两个节日中丧生。这是三个DJ的故事，他们在大屠杀开始前让他们跳舞，却失去了生命</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 11:01:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/these-djs-survived-hamas-massacre-to-tell-the-tale-and-play-another-set/0000018b-7351-d4a8-a3cf-fff9e9380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯战争中绝望情绪加剧，数千人闯入加沙的联合国仓库</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article/thousands-break-into-un-warehouses-in-gaza-as-desperation-grows-amid-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-7ab6-d1da-a1bb-7fbef8c70000</link><description>以色列对加沙的猛烈空袭和围困导致供电中断，居民在战争不断升级的情况下几乎没有食物、燃料或水。加沙人闯入联合国援助仓库拿走“基本生存物品”</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 10:18:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article/thousands-break-into-un-warehouses-in-gaza-as-desperation-grows-amid-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-7ab6-d1da-a1bb-7fbef8c70000</guid></item><item><title>“希望的空间”：前美国人质对被哈马斯俘虏的以色列人提出建议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ex-u-s-hostage-calls-on-israel-to-show-greater-leadership-for-those-held-by-hamas/0000018b-7a8d-d0f6-afeb-7a9df6ab0000</link><description>艾伦·格罗斯 (Alan Gross) 被错误地关押在古巴监狱五年，他向被关押在加沙的 229 个有亲人的家庭发出了一条信息，同时也向内塔尼亚胡政府发出了一条信息，他批评内塔尼亚胡政府没有采取足够的措施来帮助他们</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 09:29:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ex-u-s-hostage-calls-on-israel-to-show-greater-leadership-for-those-held-by-hamas/0000018b-7a8d-d0f6-afeb-7a9df6ab0000</guid></item><item><title>愤怒之后，内塔尼亚胡删除了指责安全负责人发动哈马斯袭击的帖子并道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article/after-drawing-fury-netanyahu-deletes-tweet-blaming-security-chiefs-for-hamas-attack/0000018b-7a77-d4a8-a3cf-feff35d20000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡周六晚上在一篇帖子中声称，他从未收到过有关哈马斯致命袭击的预警。他早些时候表示，“战后每个人都必须回答难题……现在，我的任务是拯救国家”</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 08:35:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article/after-drawing-fury-netanyahu-deletes-tweet-blaming-security-chiefs-for-hamas-attack/0000018b-7a77-d4a8-a3cf-feff35d20000</guid></item><item><title>众议院议长迈克·约翰逊在共和党犹太会议上表示：“上帝并没有结束与以色列的关系”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article/.premium/house-speaker-mike-johnson-tells-gop-jewish-confab-god-is-not-done-with-israel/0000018b-79c6-d4a8-a3cf-fdef927d0000</link><description>新当选的福音派基督教公共发言人承诺在与哈马斯的战争中坚定支持以色列，并表示“当哈马斯不再对以色列构成威胁时，将会停火”</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 06:01:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article/.premium/house-speaker-mike-johnson-tells-gop-jewish-confab-god-is-not-done-with-israel/0000018b-79c6-d4a8-a3cf-fdef927d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队击落向以色列北部发射的火箭弹；火箭击中基亚特什莫纳的家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article-live/netanyahu-asserts-he-was-not-warned-about-possibility-of-war-meets-hostages-families/0000018b-797e-d4a8-a3cf-fdff76a30000</link><description>以色列国防军：袭击加沙450个目标，人道主义援助增加 ■ 内塔尼亚胡删除了指责哈马斯袭击安全负责人的推文 ■ 数千名加沙人闯入联合国仓库，偷窃面粉和卫生用品 ■ 阿联酋和沙特阿拉伯谴责在加沙的地面行动 ■自 10 月 7 日以来，至少 1,300 人被哈马斯杀害 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：8,005 名加沙人被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 05:24:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article-live/netanyahu-asserts-he-was-not-warned-about-possibility-of-war-meets-hostages-families/0000018b-797e-d4a8-a3cf-fdff76a30000</guid></item><it